data.description: Come Home to over 10 Rolling, Wooded, Acres.  This Beautiful 3-bed, 2.5 Bath Home is the Perfect Country Retreat. It Features: Open Floor Plan, New Granite Counter Tops, White Wood Cabinets, Electric HeatPump, Electric water heater, New (23) windows, Large 2-car Attached Garage, Barn, Over sized septic system designed for a family of 12, Large Deck for relaxing or entertaining, a huge garden, a cistern to keep Your Plants Growing, and plenty of quiet and privacy.  Hurry out to see this Beautiful Home. Bring your comfy shoes so you can hike the property. This Oasis Will Not Last!
